    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-post-js",
    "path": "/2022-11-08--nl-cy-prediction/",
    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Celestial Symphony","author":"ふぇいと"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9fc1c2a6-cf4e-5c8e-8ea7-1fb596c7ab30","excerpt":"ワールドシリーズも終わり、オフシーズンに本格突入しましたが、\n各Awardsのファイナリストが発表されましたね。\nこの記事ではNational LeagueのCy Young賞の展望をセイバーメトリクス系指標を参照しながら見ていこうと思います。 まず、NLのCY賞ファイナリストは以下の3名です。 Sandy…","html":"<style type=\"text/css\">\n<!--\np {white-space: pre-wrap}\nsection {width:100%; float: left;}\ndiv.album_cover {float: left; width:50%;}\ndiv.album_info {float: left; width:50%; padding-left:10px;}\ndiv.album_meta {padding-bottom: 10px;}\ndiv.tracklist {padding-top: 10px;}\ntable,tr,th,td {border: none;}\nth,tr,td {line-height: 1.0em !important;}\n-->\n</style>\n<p>ワールドシリーズも終わり、オフシーズンに本格突入しましたが、\n各Awardsのファイナリストが発表されましたね。\nこの記事ではNational LeagueのCy Young賞の展望をセイバーメトリクス系指標を参照しながら見ていこうと思います。</p>\n<p>まず、NLのCY賞ファイナリストは以下の3名です。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Your 2022 NL Cy Young Award finalists! <a href=\"https://t.co/ppOKtL9lAT\">pic.twitter.com/ppOKtL9lAT</a></p>&mdash; MLB (@MLB) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MLB/status/1589756169501167616?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mlb.com/player/sandy-alcantara-645261\">Sandy Alcantara</a> (MIA)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mlb.com/player/max-fried-608331\">Max Fried</a> (ATL)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mlb.com/es/player/julio-urias-628711\">Julio Urías</a> (LAD)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>AlcantaraとFriedは予想通りですが、Uriasが残ったのはかなり意外でしたね。\nAaron NolaやCarlos Rodónのほうが残るかと予想していました。</p>\n<p>それでは3人の投球内容、指標を見ていきましょう。</p>\n<h1>ファイナリスト3人の指標比較</h1>\n<p>Alcantara, Fried, Uriasの主要指標の比較表を以下に掲載します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 673px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.76954732510288%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/fc615/stats_table.avif 243w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/b3175/stats_table.avif 485w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/285c0/stats_table.avif 673w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 673px) 100vw, 673px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/0e3e2/stats_table.webp 243w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/749af/stats_table.webp 485w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/b8cf5/stats_table.webp 673w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 673px) 100vw, 673px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/8aea6/stats_table.png 243w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/44c61/stats_table.png 485w,\n/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/c391c/stats_table.png 673w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 673px) 100vw, 673px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/78b551d8f0eb8e36fc7f38d42ae4fc44/c391c/stats_table.png\"\n            alt=\"stats table\"\n            title=\"stats table\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>ここから見える3人の特徴を列挙していきましょう。</p>\n<h2>Sandy Alcantara</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>3人中1位の指標は意外と少ない(tERAとxwOBAくらい、xwOBAは僅差)</li>\n<li>しかし<strong>2位の指標が非常に多い(9個)</strong></li>\n<li>特筆すべきは<strong>ダントツに多いイニング数</strong>。228イニングは現代のMLBにおいて突出している</li>\n<li>イニング数の多さと、総合的な指標の優秀さから<strong>fWAR, bWARともに3人中トップ</strong></li>\n<li>文句をつけられるとすればHardHit%の高さか</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Max Fried</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Barrel%とBB%の低さが突出。「ホームラン性の打球を打たれず、四球も出さない」エースの投球。</li>\n<li>FIP,xFIPなどdefense-independentな指標がトップのものが多い。「ホームラン/三振/四球」の観点からは最も優れていると言っていいだろう</li>\n<li>LOB％とBABIPが悪い(特にBABIP)。守備や運の要素でERAが悪化している可能性がある\n<ul>\n<li>それでも2.48という十分以上に高水準なERAに抑えているのは流石</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Alcantaraには負けているものの、fWAR,bWARともに高水準</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Julio Urias</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>ERAが突出(NLトップ)</li>\n<li>FIP/xFIPは残り2人よりもかなり悪い</li>\n<li>BABIP,LOB%がかなり良い(Friedと真逆)\n<ul>\n<li>ERAが低い最大の理由と考えられる。</li>\n<li>LADの投手は数年単位でこの傾向があり、走者を出しても失点しない特徴が際立っている</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>HardHit%も3人中トップ\n<ul>\n<li>これもHardHitを重要視するLADらしさを感じる</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>純粋な投手の能力で見るとAlcantara,Friedには負けるが、「失点しないこと」も投手の能力と捉えるならば非常に優秀な成績ではある</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Statcastデータ</h1>\n<p>3人のStatcastのデータも貼っておきましょう。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.27160493827161%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/fc615/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.avif 243w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/b3175/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.avif 485w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/006d3/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.avif 970w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/9f90b/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.avif 1270w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/0e3e2/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.webp 243w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/749af/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.webp 485w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/dbca2/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.webp 970w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/3979e/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.webp 1270w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/8aea6/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.png 243w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/44c61/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.png 485w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/587b0/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.png 970w,\n/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/e8e04/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.png 1270w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/59e4d82cb43f33d743a8fef3bd92b04a/587b0/20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast.png\"\n            alt=\"20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast\"\n            title=\"20221108SandyAlcantaraStatcast\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.68312757201646%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/fc615/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.avif 243w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/b3175/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.avif 485w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/006d3/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.avif 970w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/53415/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.avif 1268w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/0e3e2/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.webp 243w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/749af/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.webp 485w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/dbca2/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.webp 970w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/144c0/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.webp 1268w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/8aea6/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.png 243w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/44c61/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.png 485w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/587b0/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.png 970w,\n/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/bc3ae/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.png 1268w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b4c1209defd409c9b4218f4508fe2112/587b0/20221108MaxFriedStatcast.png\"\n            alt=\"20221108MaxFriedStatcast\"\n            title=\"20221108MaxFriedStatcast\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.68312757201646%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/fc615/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.avif 243w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/b3175/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.avif 485w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/006d3/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.avif 970w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/1ae2a/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.avif 1266w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/0e3e2/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.webp 243w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/749af/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.webp 485w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/dbca2/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.webp 970w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/da80b/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.webp 1266w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/8aea6/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.png 243w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/44c61/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.png 485w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/587b0/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.png 970w,\n/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/8b70b/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.png 1266w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d12072f000fdb4c90279f906cdd400ef/587b0/20221108JulioUriasStatcast.png\"\n            alt=\"20221108JulioUriasStatcast\"\n            title=\"20221108JulioUriasStatcast\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>FriedはBarrel%,BB%,HardHit%の優秀さが、UriasはHardHit%とFastball Spinの優秀さが際立っていますね。\nAlcantaraは速球の球速と総合力という感じ。</p>\n<h1>結論めいたもの</h1>\n<p>直感的な印象と同様に、「まぁAlcantaraが優勢だよね」という気はします。\n総合的に優れていると上でも書きましたが、bWARとfWARで大きく差をつけてトップというのは大きい。\nただMax Friedも指標面では善戦してるのではと思いますね。\nATLファンとしてはCYには届かなくともなるべく多くの票を獲得してほしい。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/2022-11-08--nl-cy-prediction/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"セイバー指標で見る2022NL Cy Young賞見通し","date":"2022, Nov 08","tags":[],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAIAAADwazoUAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAOElEQVQoz93QwQkAMAgEQfsvVzgODzWBdBACebj/+ayth2wSBuDukiKCZGZeYJIAqkqn7p4/7AfefWSQp0h8zgwAAAAASUVORK5CYII="},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/afa5c/no-image.png","srcSet":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/0dee1/no-image.png 750w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/8beaa/no-image.png 1080w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/d079a/no-image.png 1366w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/afa5c/no-image.png 1920w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/ba386/no-image.avif 750w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/8adb1/no-image.avif 1080w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/dc6b3/no-image.avif 1366w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/031aa/no-image.avif 1920w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/a66aa/no-image.webp 750w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/65dd5/no-image.webp 1080w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/4fad6/no-image.webp 1366w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/c512e/no-image.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.5625}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2022-11-08--nl-cy-prediction/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2022-10-02--netlify-to-github-pages/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"NetlifyからGithub Pagesに移行した","tags":["web","Gatsby","Github Pages"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAIAAADwazoUAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAOElEQVQoz93QwQkAMAgEQfsvVzgODzWBdBACebj/+ayth2wSBuDukiKCZGZeYJIAqkqn7p4/7AfefWSQp0h8zgwAAAAASUVORK5CYII="},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/afa5c/no-image.png","srcSet":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/0dee1/no-image.png 750w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/8beaa/no-image.png 1080w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/d079a/no-image.png 1366w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/afa5c/no-image.png 1920w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/a66aa/no-image.webp 750w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/65dd5/no-image.webp 1080w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/4fad6/no-image.webp 1366w,\n/static/842cd26adb7c466b796e11c827fba35c/c512e/no-image.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.5625}}}}},"next":null}},
